{"tid":1268474,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美解除對華為禁令 華為可採購美零件、用Android","createTime":"2019-06-30T09:54:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T10:26:48.000Z","uid":66271,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4493419da2f942605e7041c1b07f24b20b9bb49f","tid":1268474,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:54:37.000Z","msg":"在 G20 峰會當中，美國總統特朗普公佈，正式解除對華為的禁令，使華為可繼續採購美國零件與技術合作，亦可繼續使用含有 Google 服務的 Android 手機作業系統。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2019-06-30-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%885.32.21-1280x717.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2019-06-30-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25885.32.21-1280x717.png&h=beecc70e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普在 G20 峰會與中國國家主席習近平會面後向傳媒表示，將解除對華為輸出零件、技術的禁令，允許美國企業向華為出售高科技設備。消息指中國將以採購美國產品，作為交換條件，以解除美國對額外價值 3000 億元的產品加徵稅項，以及一連串禁令。有消息指中國向美國採購了 54.4 萬噸大豆。<br />\n<br />\n在昨日舉行的新聞發表會中，中國外交部特使王小龍向傳媒重申，華為是一間私營企業，中國將歡迎美國對華為解除限制。"},{"pid":"fcfc668d78a1174654e479daf994133477dc5b2d","tid":1268474,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:00:28.000Z","msg":"美國佬驚左華為os華為cpu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e3dd6bf000b9fe300b2a06e359726d52fa605f","tid":1268474,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:14:18.000Z","msg":"聽日加你50%"},{"pid":"1f9d11f189381e49938503494d9d19d2a7ce6e7d","tid":1268474,"uid":186087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:18:45.000Z","msg":"侵侵下馬威。巧威威"},{"pid":"f0a6d62b82666d83a8e3bec97e2b295a1e7d64cd","tid":1268474,"uid":165442,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:26:48.000Z","msg":"垃圾 得個嚇字<br />\n大陸仔唔驚你就鳩縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}